      "title": "GR to return to SL on Saturday",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Former President Gotabaya Rajapaksa will return back to the country on Saturday, a source close to him said.",
        "The Former President fled the county following mass agitations calling for his resignation on July 9. He is currently in Thailand.",
        "President Ranil Wickremesinghe made arrangements for his return upon a request by Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna (SLPP). (Kelum Bandara)"
      ],
